com.adobe.aemds.guide.common

Class GuideNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.cq.sightly.WCMUsePojo
      • com.adobe.aemds.guide.common.GuideNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FDField, StyledFDField, Serializable, org.apache.sling.scripting.sightly.pojo.Use
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ESign, GuideContainer, GuideField, GuideItemsContainer, Summary, Verify

    @Model
public class GuideNode
extends com.adobe.cq.sightly.WCMUsePojo
implements Serializable, StyledFDField
    GuideNode is base class which every AEM form component inherits from. It abstracts the basic properties of each component(panel/field).Few are listed below:
    • Sling HTTP Servlet Request
    • Resource
    • Properties of the resource

    This provides basic getter's and setter's required to create/initialize and AEM Form Component.

    Since:
    AEM 6.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
